Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Report uncovers CIA murder plots
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z97zk
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Nov 1975
Startling evidence of CIA plots to assassinate foreign leaders uncovered in Senate interim report. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less